headline: Major public waste companies spent nearly $11B on M&A in 2024
summary: WM drove major spending with its $7.2 billion Stericycle deal in 2024. Republic Services, Waste Connections, GFL Environmental and Casella Waste Systems also completed numerous deals during the year.
